('Wood Cutter Clicker', 3, 'Wood Cutter Clicker is an addictive idle clicker game where you chop trees, collect wood, and upgrade your axe to become the ultimate lumberjack. With endless levels and progressive challenges, this casual tree-cutting simulator offers nonstop tapping action and resource management. Perfect for fans of clicker, idle, and tycoon games, it blends fast-paced gameplay with satisfying upgrades and wood-cutting mechanics. Build your cutting speed, unlock new tools, and see how far your chopping skills can take you.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('space asteroids war', 4, 'This game is a modern remake of the classic Asteroids, bringing fast-paced arcade action to the browser. Players control a small triangular spaceship navigating through a star-filled sky, tasked with blasting apart drifting asteroids before they collide with the ship. Each destroyed rock splits into smaller fragments, increasing both challenge and excitement. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.poki76.com/''&gt;https://www.poki76.com/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Use the Arrow Keys to navigate uarr applies thrust and activates the ship rsquo s flame while larr and rarr rotate the ship left or right Press Spacebar or Left Mouse Click to fire bullets directly from the ship rsquo s tip producing a quick am', 'English'),
('Celebrity Selen All Around The Fashion', 5, 'Welcome to Celebrity Selen All Around The Fashion. Celebrity Selen plans to try different fashion trends. She needs some help to choose the perfect costumes and outfits. Browse her wardrobe and choose the perfect outfits for each fashion trend. Play and have fun with this new game!', 'Left Mouse Button Click', 'English'),
('Space Shooter War', 6, 'Space Shooter is a classic arcade-style game where the player pilots a spaceship and faces endless waves of enemies. The main objective is to destroy as many enemy ships as possible, avoid incoming projectiles, and survive for as long as you can. The spaceship can be controlled with the keyboard or mouse, and every laser shot counts in the battle for survival. As the game progresses, difficulty increases with faster and more aggressive enemies, keeping the adrenaline high and the challenge engaging. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.ovigames.com/''&gt;https://www.ovigames.com/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Move the mouse on the canvas to move bull Click hold to shoot bull Arrows A D and Space also work bull Touch drag finger horizontally hold to fire', 'English'),
('CANDY MATCH 3 KIT 2025', 7, 'Candy Match 3 is a fun and addictive puzzle game that challenges your mind while satisfying your sweet tooth! Match three or more colorful candies in a row to clear the board and unlock exciting power-ups. With each level, the puzzles get trickier, keeping you entertained for hours of gameplay. Features: Bright and vibrant candy-themed graphics Easy to play, hard to master mechanics Special boosters and combos for extra fun Hundreds of challenging levels Relaxing gameplay perfect for all ages Get ready to swap, match, and crush your way through a world full of sugary puzzles. Play Candy Match 3 now and see how far you can go!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Ultimate Bottle Flip Game', 8, 'Offline Master Bottle 3D: Tap, Flip &amp;amp; Jump, the ultimate bottle flipping adventure where excitement meets challenge! Master the art of flipping a water bottle and embark on an exhilarating parkour frenzy. Tap to flip, spin, and jump your bottle to achieve your goals. With endless tricks and challenges, this bottle game is sure to keep you hooked! FEATURES - Stunning Graphics: Immerse yourself in visually striking bottle flipping action. - Diverse Challenges: Tackle a wide range of challenges that test your flipping prowess. - Relax and Play: Unwind with easy tap game controls.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Jumper jam', 9, 'Gameplay is similar to the Doodle Jump game. ABOUT THE GAME Welcome to Jumper jam - an exciting arcade game where simple controls meet adrenaline-packed gameplay! Control a cute character, collect shiny coins, and set new records in this colorful browser-based game.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('PinPoint', 10, 'PinPoint is a fast-paced precision arcade game where timing is everything. With every turn, you&amp;rsquo;re given a number &amp;mdash; and that&amp;rsquo;s exactly how many arrows you must launch at a rotating circle. The challenge? Each arrow must land cleanly without colliding into the others already in place. As the circle speeds up, slows down, or even changes direction, your reflexes and focus will be put to the test. Every perfect shot pushes your score higher, while a single wrong move ends the round. Key Features: Addictive one-tap gameplay that&amp;rsquo;s easy to learn, hard to master. Dynamic rotating circles with unpredictable patterns.', 'Throw at the right time never hit another stick', 'English');
