('Sins and Desires', 13, '&amp;ldquo;Sins and Desires&amp;rdquo; is a captivating visual novel in the detective genre with romance elements. As detective Felicia, you travel to the village of West-Alben to uncover the mystery of aristocrat William&amp;rsquo;s disappearance. Experience an interactive story with branching choices, a relationship system that affects the ending, and romance routes with Albert, Felix, and Victor. The atmosphere of a dark mansion, a foggy lake, and a village full of secrets keeps you intrigued. Every choice matters - will you uncover the truth or fall into the shadows of West-Alben&amp;rsquo;s sins and desires?', 'In ldquo Sins and Desires rdquo you play as detective Felicia investigating the disappearance of an aristocrat in the village of West-Alben This is a visual novel with a mystery story romance and branching choices', 'English'),
('Fit Runner', 14, 'Welcome Gamers!! Lets play fun and Fit race and make the body from fat or fit instantly and see the cool and funny body shapes by just collecting different amount of foods and see the impact instantly.!!', '- Simple Control - Click Mouse Tap to play - Swipe Left and Right', 'English'),
('Glow Blocks', 15, 'Glow Blocks is a vibrant neon puzzle game inspired by the timeless classic Tetris. Stack glowing blocks in a futuristic grid, clear full lines, and climb through endless levels as the speed increases. With its colorful neon visuals, cyberpunk atmosphere, and smooth gameplay, Glow Blocks is both nostalgic and fresh. Challenge yourself to beat your high score, enjoy the glowing effects, and test your reflexes in this addictive endless puzzle experience!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Four in a Row', 16, 'Four in a Row is the classic strategy board game you know and love, now in a colorful digital version! Drop your red or yellow discs into the grid and try to be the first to line up four in a row - vertically, horizontally, or diagonally. Play against the computer with increasing difficulty levels or challenge a friend in local 2-player mode. With smooth gameplay, fun sound effects, and a bright cool style, this game is perfect for all ages. Can you outsmart your opponent and claim victory?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Hero Inc', 17, 'Step into a thrilling 3D adventure RPG! Control your hero, explore mysterious levels, fight dangerous enemies, and unlock powerful skills. Pass challenging quests, defeat epic bosses, and protect the world. Are you ready for the ultimate action adventure?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Farm Defense', 18, 'Survive against waves of bizarre monsters trying to invade your farm. Collect temporary power-ups like rapid fire, explosive ammo, health packs, and electric fences. At the end of each stage, pick from random upgrades, unlock new weapons, deploy crop duster airstrikes, slow enemies with traps, or grab a magnet to pull power-ups. Progress further to unlock new playable heroes with unique styles.', 'Move with Arrow Keys WASD press Space to turn around', 'English'),
('Classic Checkers: Forest', 19, 'A captivating board game set in a unique forest-themed atmosphere! Enjoy classic checkers rules surrounded by nature. Sharpen your strategic thinking, challenge friends or AI, and immerse yourself in a relaxing yet exciting experience. Perfect for all ages!', 'Dont forget to customize the game to your liking giveaway mode mandatory captures and other settings are available in the menu Choose your game mode play against the computer or share the board with a friend Move your pieces according to the classic', 'English'),
('The Mobs Farm in Mineblock!', 20, 'The legendary mob farm in Mine is back and ready to introduce you to a lot of new content right now! In the game, your goal is to upgrade your farm so that it can destroy mobs more effectively. You have access to a wide range of epic items that can help you defeat enemies faster and easier. As you defeat mobs, you will earn money that you can use to unlock new mobs, purchase new saws, and increase their damage.', 'Select the item you want to place on the game board and click on it Then select the mob you want to destroy and click on it to place it on the game board Each mob has its own health and mass and some have unique abilities Some of them can even help yo', 'English');
