('Lost Things', 25, 'Embark on an exciting adventure where your powers of observation are your main tool! This is a relaxing hidden object game created for those who appreciate slow-paced gameplay and enjoy exploring detailed worlds. Forget about time pressure! Here you can explore huge, colorful maps filled with hundreds of artfully hidden objects at your own pace. Game Features: &amp;bull; No time limit: Enjoy the search process without feeling cornered by a timer. &amp;bull; Addictive gameplay: Immerse yourself in long and exciting sessions full of discoveries and satisfaction from finding objects. &amp;bull; Visual Enjoyment: Enjoy the vivid and detailed graphics that make searching', 'New sections of the map open when a certain number of items are found When the hint is activated the camera moves to the object so that you can collect it and the object itself is highlighted with small effects The left mouse button is used to collect', 'English'),
