('Beaten Trump Face LOL', 30, 'Get ready to laugh out loud in Beaten Trump Face LOL &amp;ndash; the wacky face-deformation game where you can poke, drag, and squash Trump&amp;rsquo;s face into hilarious shapes! Stretch, bruise, and twist the photo in real time with slime-like effects, or tap and drag to add funny bumpy marks. Every interaction creates ridiculous results that you can screenshot and share with friends. Whether you want to mash, warp, or just make a goofy face, this game guarantees endless comedy moments!', 'mouse only', 'English');
