('Little bugs', 37, 'The beetles approach the two pictures and then there is a choice of which way to go. One picture is safe, you can walk through it, the second is a trapdoor into the abyss and if you misunderstand the hint in the form of a piece of vegetable or animal, you will not be able to reach the finish line.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
