('Flappy Birds Game Ai', 44, 'Flappy Bird is an incredibly simple yet frustratingly addictive mobile game. Players tap the screen to make a small, pixelated bird flap its wings and navigate through a series of green pipes. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.crazygamesfree.com/.''&gt;https://www.crazygamesfree.com/.&lt;/a&gt; The goal is to get the highest score possible by passing through as many pipes as you can without hitting them or the ground. Its challenging difficulty and retro 8-bit graphics made it an overnight sensation and a cultural phenomenon.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
