('Sonic Run for Lamborghini', 255, 'Are you ready to join the excitement in Sonic Run for Lamborghini, an amazing and free-to-play online game designed for kids? In this thrilling adventure, youll guide the iconic Sonic as he races to the other side, collecting dazzling diamonds and aiming to buy a brand-new Lamborghini! Collect diamonds and work towards that ultimate Lamborghini prize. Avoid obstacles and have a blast in this high-octane adventure!', 'WAD and mouse to draw the line', 'English'),
