('Single Line: Drawing Puzzle', 419, 'Icon image Single Line: Drawing Puzzle About this game Challenge your mind and unleash your creativity with Single Line: Drawing Puzzle! This exciting game is perfect for anyone who loves brain teasers and enjoys solving clever puzzles. Your mission is simple yet addictive: draw one continuous line to complete intricate designs without lifting your finger or retracing your steps. Are you ready to take on this one-line challenge?', '- Draw in One Go Use a single continuous line to complete the given shape - Avoid Overlaps Plan your path carefully and don rsquo t retrace any steps - Complete Shapes Solve each shape to unlock the next more challenging level', 'English'),
('DuaLight   A Reflected Game', 420, 'DuaLight is a challenging 2D pixel art hyper-casual platformer. The true path lies in the reflection. Navigate levels where the real world tricks your eyes, and only those who watch the reflection below can move forward. Minimalist and short. In DuaLight &amp;ndash; A Reflected Game, nothing is as it seems&amp;hellip; or rather, everything only appears in the reflection. You control a character in a world where invisible platforms can&amp;rsquo;t be seen in the real world, but only in the reflection below the screen. You&amp;rsquo;ll encounter spikes and invisible platforms until you look at the reflection and realize the path was there all along.', 'Use the W A S D keys or the arrow keys to move Press W the up arrow or the spacebar to jump Press P to return to menu', 'English');
